Class AbstractBulkResources<T extends DataObjectRestRep>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.vipr.client.core.AbstractResources<T>
      • com.emc.vipr.client.core.AbstractBulkResources<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of resource.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    BulkResources<T>, Resources<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractCatalogBulkResources, AbstractCoreBulkResources, CustomConfigs, TasksResources

    public abstract class AbstractBulkResources<T extends DataObjectRestRep>
extends AbstractResources<T>
implements BulkResources<T>
    Base class for all resources types that support bulk operations. This overrides the getByIds(Collection, ResourceFilter) method to query through the bulk API for improved performance.
